WEBVTT

01:31.650 --> 01:35.009
[How dare you!?]

01:35.080 --> 01:37.970
[Episode 4]

01:38.060 --> 01:43.030
[Changning Palace]

01:50.870 --> 01:52.000
Your Highness, run!

01:52.430 --> 01:53.890
It shouldn't be like this.

01:54.430 --> 01:56.200
This wasn't the plan.

01:57.789 --> 01:58.640
Xu Yao!

01:58.870 --> 01:59.470
Don't die.

02:00.400 --> 02:01.070
Please.

02:01.280 --> 02:03.810
Your Highness,
do you really not understand?

02:04.150 --> 02:04.710
Run!

02:05.230 --> 02:07.360
Don't look back no matter who you meet.

02:07.680 --> 02:08.360
Stay alive.

02:10.000 --> 02:11.840
Are you hurt anywhere, Your Highness?

02:11.840 --> 02:12.910
Trust no one.

02:17.710 --> 02:18.570
Don't leave me.

02:21.590 --> 02:22.470
Don't leave me.

02:25.560 --> 02:26.090
I'm here.

02:40.710 --> 02:41.510
Your Majesty.

02:41.680 --> 02:43.480
The arsonists have been caught.

02:47.910 --> 02:51.560
Your Majesty, we're innocent!

02:51.910 --> 02:53.560
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

02:53.560 --> 02:54.560
I am innocent!

02:55.190 --> 02:56.520
We were just passing by.

02:56.520 --> 02:58.030
We saw the library was on fire.

02:58.030 --> 02:59.290
So we went to put it out!

02:59.680 --> 03:01.680
The library is in a remote location.

03:01.870 --> 03:03.800
It wasn't even your shift that day.

03:03.800 --> 03:05.260
What were you doing there?

03:05.710 --> 03:07.800
Spare us, Your Majesty!

03:07.800 --> 03:08.560
It wasn't me!

03:08.560 --> 03:09.400
Spare us, Your Majesty!

03:09.400 --> 03:10.150
It wasn't me!

03:10.430 --> 03:11.800
-Your Majesty, spare my life!
-Your Majesty, spare my life!

03:11.800 --> 03:12.400
Kill them!

03:12.430 --> 03:14.470
-Your Majesty, spare my life!
-Your Majesty!

03:14.470 --> 03:15.270
Your Majesty!

03:15.680 --> 03:16.230
Your Majesty!

03:16.230 --> 03:18.760
-Your Majesty, spare my life!
-Your Majesty!

03:21.750 --> 03:22.520
Please!

03:22.750 --> 03:25.680
-Your Majesty, spare my life!
-Please spare my life!

03:56.190 --> 03:57.250
Does it still hurt?

04:18.160 --> 04:18.760
Tissue...

04:19.720 --> 04:20.320
Tissue...

04:21.390 --> 04:22.250
Handkerchief!

04:22.270 --> 04:23.530
Hurry! Handkerchief!

04:39.600 --> 04:40.260
You can cry.

04:41.270 --> 04:42.200
It's okay to cry.

04:43.500 --> 04:45.360
You'll feel better after crying.

04:56.680 --> 04:59.140
Everyone from the library
has been rescued.

05:00.000 --> 05:01.730
The arsonists have been found.

05:01.800 --> 05:02.330
However,

05:03.450 --> 05:04.910
they're just scapegoats.

05:05.720 --> 05:06.310
I believe

05:07.750 --> 05:09.950
they were acting on Xiahou Bo's orders.

05:14.360 --> 05:16.510
Senior Minister Xu has been brought back.

05:16.510 --> 05:18.390
To avoid Prince Duan's spies,

05:19.430 --> 05:22.230
he's been temporarily placed
at a suburban house.

05:22.240 --> 05:23.640
When things settle down,

05:25.000 --> 05:25.930
we'll go see him.

05:34.430 --> 05:35.430
What about Xu Yao?

05:45.630 --> 05:46.560
The coroner said

05:47.250 --> 05:48.190
he died

05:48.950 --> 05:49.870
in peace.

05:51.430 --> 05:53.030
Before the fire reached him,

05:54.680 --> 05:56.480
he had already died from poison.

05:58.240 --> 05:58.920
So

06:00.270 --> 06:01.600
he didn't suffer again.

06:18.360 --> 06:19.760
Take the medicine first.

06:20.680 --> 06:21.880
It's not hot anymore.

06:22.720 --> 06:23.560
Just drink it

06:25.000 --> 06:26.800
like water to reduce your fever.

06:39.830 --> 06:40.690
Thank goodness

06:41.750 --> 06:43.610
you also came from another world.

06:44.510 --> 06:46.040
Otherwise I'd be all alone.

07:04.830 --> 07:06.870
I just said no one would harm you,

07:07.750 --> 07:08.410
and then...

07:13.160 --> 07:13.760
I'm sorry.

07:15.680 --> 07:16.740
I broke my promise.

07:21.600 --> 07:23.600
You don't have to wait until the end.

07:24.870 --> 07:26.730
If it becomes too painful for you,

07:26.830 --> 07:27.240
I...

07:29.750 --> 07:30.600
I mean...

07:35.070 --> 07:36.530
I can send you out right now

07:37.750 --> 07:39.210
to get away from this mess.

07:48.510 --> 07:49.909
Do you want to leave here?

07:59.430 --> 08:00.560
I've recorded all

08:00.560 --> 08:02.070
of Prince Duan's plans in a book

08:02.070 --> 08:04.890
and buried it under the window
of his mansion's back kitchen.

08:04.890 --> 08:06.480
Don't go looking for it right away.

08:06.480 --> 08:07.950
Wait at least seven days.

08:10.870 --> 08:12.480
Xu Yao said he left a book

08:13.270 --> 08:15.330
that can be used against Prince Duan.

08:19.360 --> 08:20.310
You mean...

08:20.720 --> 08:22.430
We can't let Xu Yao die in vain.

08:26.270 --> 08:27.270
You mean

08:29.290 --> 08:31.150
you don't need me to send you away?

08:33.530 --> 08:34.960
Why is that your focus?

08:34.980 --> 08:36.630
I'm talking about Xu Yao's book

08:36.630 --> 08:38.070
that can be used against Prince Duan.

08:38.070 --> 08:40.270
You've missed such an important point.

08:45.390 --> 08:45.840
Right.

08:50.270 --> 08:50.730
What...

08:51.550 --> 08:52.360
What book?

08:56.080 --> 08:57.280
Before he died, Xu Yao

08:57.360 --> 08:58.480
said he had recorded Prince Duan's plans

08:58.480 --> 08:59.360
in a book

08:59.750 --> 09:02.280
and hid it right inside
the prince's mansion.

09:02.390 --> 09:03.590
He came specifically

09:03.840 --> 09:05.040
to tell me about this.

09:05.790 --> 09:08.200
That's why,
despite being severely poisoned,

09:08.200 --> 09:11.530
he risked his life to bring this message
to me in the library.

09:11.790 --> 09:13.510
I can't believe I actually thought

09:13.510 --> 09:15.370
our plan had succeeded back then.

09:17.720 --> 09:19.980
Xu Yao was kept in the dark
his whole life,

09:20.550 --> 09:22.080
slaving away for his enemy.

09:22.080 --> 09:23.410
Is that somehow better?

09:24.630 --> 09:25.270
At least

09:26.440 --> 09:28.440
he could determine his own fate,

09:31.630 --> 09:32.390
unlike those

09:34.440 --> 09:36.440
who have no control over their fate.

09:39.120 --> 09:40.320
No control over fate.

09:42.390 --> 09:43.920
Are you talking about Xu Yao

09:44.000 --> 09:45.030
or yourself?

09:51.150 --> 09:51.840
I mean

09:54.910 --> 09:55.970
the road is winding

09:56.570 --> 09:57.970
but the future is bright.

09:59.550 --> 10:00.350
You're right.

10:01.400 --> 10:03.330
The most important thing for us now

10:03.440 --> 10:04.510
is to survive.

10:07.160 --> 10:08.360
Our main goal

10:09.200 --> 10:10.120
is to survive.

10:11.550 --> 10:14.150
Who says you need to be
a warrior to win the game?

10:14.390 --> 10:15.790
If we survive till the end,

10:15.790 --> 10:17.120
we'll have everything.

10:17.910 --> 10:18.480
Next,

10:20.120 --> 10:21.240
we need to play

10:21.550 --> 10:23.150
a game of survival overtime.

10:27.690 --> 10:28.750
Do you understand?

10:29.120 --> 10:29.920
I understand.

10:31.540 --> 10:32.670
I fully understand.

10:34.910 --> 10:35.440
Survive.

10:38.760 --> 10:39.590
Survive!

10:48.120 --> 10:50.240
Why won't His Highness
come to see me in person?

10:50.240 --> 10:51.100
Your Highness.

10:51.600 --> 10:53.600
His Highness is ill and cannot come.

10:54.200 --> 10:54.730
He's ill?

10:58.240 --> 10:59.050
How come?

11:00.440 --> 11:01.200
To be honest,

11:01.910 --> 11:03.720
when the library caught fire that day,

11:03.720 --> 11:05.030
the one who escaped from the fire

11:05.030 --> 11:06.290
was Consort Yu Wanyin,

11:06.790 --> 11:08.520
and the one who couldn't escape

11:08.670 --> 11:10.270
was His Highness's adviser,

11:10.440 --> 11:11.030
Xu Yao.

11:12.030 --> 11:12.960
What did you say?

11:15.030 --> 11:17.090
Yu Wanyin and His Highness's adviser

11:17.200 --> 11:18.600
were both in the library?

11:21.080 --> 11:22.390
Why didn't he tell me?

11:23.720 --> 11:25.840
Is there something
he couldn't bring himself to say?

11:25.840 --> 11:27.900
He had intended to keep this from you,

11:28.200 --> 11:29.600
fearing that the more you knew,

11:29.600 --> 11:31.120
the more likely
you would get into trouble.

11:31.120 --> 11:34.740
Her Majesty now holds absolute power
and is at the height of her influence.

11:34.740 --> 11:37.630
She already sees His Highness as a thorn
in her side and targets him at every turn.

11:37.630 --> 11:38.960
That tyrant and his demonic consort

11:38.960 --> 11:42.040
are also doing everything they can
to cut off His Highness's support.

11:42.040 --> 11:44.640
His Highness is now isolated
and without help.

11:44.960 --> 11:46.030
Your Highness,

11:46.600 --> 11:48.530
please take good care of yourself.

11:51.840 --> 11:53.390
His Highness has the world in his heart

11:53.390 --> 11:54.790
and cares for all people.

11:56.000 --> 11:58.260
He's truly destined to rule this empire.

11:58.510 --> 12:01.040
Now he's hindered
by treacherous officials.

12:01.120 --> 12:03.050
How could I stand by and do nothing?

12:06.480 --> 12:08.280
Although I cannot often see him,

12:09.790 --> 12:10.440
I

12:11.480 --> 12:13.150
think of him constantly.

12:15.750 --> 12:16.810
Please, young man,

12:17.790 --> 12:19.850
deliver this letter to His Highness.

12:20.550 --> 12:22.410
It'll surely help him rise again.

12:32.430 --> 12:35.240
The library caught fire a few days ago.

12:36.080 --> 12:37.340
Is everyone all right?

12:37.720 --> 12:38.520
Your Majesty.

12:38.960 --> 12:40.320
The imperial physician said

12:40.320 --> 12:42.550
that Consort Yu's burns were not serious,

12:42.550 --> 12:43.270
but that day

12:43.630 --> 12:45.320
after jumping from the third floor
into the water,

12:45.320 --> 12:46.780
she had also caught a cold.

12:46.790 --> 12:50.120
Thus, she had been running a high fever
for the past few days.

12:52.200 --> 12:54.840
Jumping from the third floor
into the water?

12:58.840 --> 13:00.510
She's quite brave, isn't she?

13:01.120 --> 13:02.030
Her external injuries have healed,

13:02.030 --> 13:04.230
but I fear the shock she experienced...

13:06.030 --> 13:07.360
What about His Majesty?

13:07.390 --> 13:08.480
Has he visited her?

13:09.600 --> 13:12.960
It was His Majesty who carried Consort Yu
back to the palace that day.

13:12.960 --> 13:14.600
But for some reason these past few days,

13:14.600 --> 13:16.330
he hasn't gone to see her again.

13:20.470 --> 13:22.470
Consort Yu was saved by Prince Duan.

13:22.790 --> 13:23.910
His Majesty is suspicious by nature.

13:23.910 --> 13:26.040
Perhaps this has caused some discord.

13:30.120 --> 13:31.430
Oh, how interesting!

13:32.630 --> 13:33.600
I've also heard

13:34.030 --> 13:36.240
that Consort Yu's palace
has been ransacked,

13:36.240 --> 13:36.870
as if

13:37.320 --> 13:39.120
she's about to fall out of favor.

13:41.850 --> 13:43.200
I can't miss out on

13:43.790 --> 13:45.510
such a good show.

13:48.070 --> 13:52.490
[Changning Palace]

13:53.670 --> 13:54.270
My Lady.

13:58.240 --> 13:59.840
My Lady, are you alright now?

14:01.120 --> 14:02.120
I'm fine now.

14:02.440 --> 14:04.170
My Lady, you're still smiling!

14:04.600 --> 14:06.320
His Majesty hasn't come to see you lately,

14:06.320 --> 14:08.240
and those servants
are taking advantage of it.

14:08.240 --> 14:10.900
They've taken away
more than half of our things.

14:11.670 --> 14:12.150
Really?

14:14.440 --> 14:16.630
The Empress Dowager has arrived!

14:19.010 --> 14:20.810
Why is the Empress Dowager here?

14:21.320 --> 14:23.120
I heard the library caught fire.

14:23.750 --> 14:25.410
Were you injured, Consort Yu?

14:26.510 --> 14:27.080
I'm fine.

14:28.150 --> 14:30.480
I was concerned about you
and came to see you.

14:30.480 --> 14:32.280
Do you know who started the fire?

14:33.320 --> 14:34.270
I don't know.

14:35.440 --> 14:37.910
You've been far too ostentatious,

14:38.120 --> 14:39.910
which is why you've earned envy.

14:39.910 --> 14:41.110
After this incident,

14:42.120 --> 14:43.360
you should know

14:44.200 --> 14:47.320
that the Emperor will not protect you.

14:48.360 --> 14:49.160
Yes, yes, yes.

14:51.030 --> 14:52.270
This is so sudden.

14:52.510 --> 14:55.510
Eunuch An, where will we live?

14:55.720 --> 14:57.440
Don't worry, ladies.

14:57.630 --> 14:59.350
Accommodations
have already been arranged for you.

14:59.350 --> 15:00.000
Eunuch An.

15:00.200 --> 15:01.620
Just tell us where we'll be staying.

15:01.620 --> 15:02.270
Yes, please.

15:02.270 --> 15:03.550
I haven't finished packing my things.

15:03.550 --> 15:04.150
Eunuch An.

15:05.670 --> 15:07.360
Women in this imperial harem

15:08.150 --> 15:09.080
are all the same.

15:18.150 --> 15:18.810
To the left.

15:20.510 --> 15:21.170
To the left.

15:23.320 --> 15:24.120
To the left...

15:28.360 --> 15:29.090
To the right.

15:40.750 --> 15:41.870
Arrange everything by category.

15:41.870 --> 15:43.080
Place the furniture neatly.

15:43.080 --> 15:43.810
Every corner

15:44.120 --> 15:45.250
must be free of dust.

15:46.000 --> 15:46.460
Vulgar.

15:46.600 --> 15:47.270
Too elegant.

15:47.270 --> 15:48.670
Both vulgar and elegant.

15:49.080 --> 15:50.010
This one is nice.

15:53.960 --> 15:56.090
Why make the chamber pot so beautiful?

16:06.870 --> 16:08.530
How many times have I told you?

16:08.600 --> 16:10.260
Consort Yu doesn't like blue.

16:10.480 --> 16:11.640
What are you doing?

16:11.870 --> 16:13.800
Noble Consort Wei is ostentatious

16:14.000 --> 16:16.860
simply because
she flaunts her family background.

16:19.440 --> 16:20.270
It is green.

16:22.080 --> 16:22.460
Is it?

16:26.440 --> 16:26.900
Really?

16:27.600 --> 16:28.660
Yes, Your Majesty.

16:36.440 --> 16:37.970
In my opinion, the lighting

16:38.080 --> 16:39.750
affects how colors appear.

16:41.750 --> 16:42.810
Yes, Your Majesty.

16:44.790 --> 16:45.870
If you obey me,

16:46.320 --> 16:48.080
I will naturally care for you.

16:48.960 --> 16:49.620
Otherwise,

16:50.000 --> 16:52.720
in these dark chambers,

16:53.440 --> 16:54.960
when will you ever rise up?

16:55.670 --> 16:56.600
Your Majesty.

16:58.030 --> 16:59.320
What are you doing here?

16:59.320 --> 17:01.720
I'm here to announce His Majesty's decree.

17:02.550 --> 17:05.880
Congratulations, Consort Yu
has been promoted to Noble Consort

17:05.880 --> 17:07.510
and will move to Zhaoyang Palace.

17:07.510 --> 17:08.369
Your Highness,

17:08.880 --> 17:09.550
please.

17:12.200 --> 17:13.060
Noble Consort?

17:19.510 --> 17:21.160
How spacious!

17:22.109 --> 17:23.750
How magnificent!

17:24.589 --> 17:26.310
How beautiful!

17:28.590 --> 17:29.390
Do you like it?

17:29.640 --> 17:31.040
It's exclusively yours.

17:31.200 --> 17:31.860
Exclusive.

17:33.830 --> 17:35.090
This is too exclusive.

17:35.790 --> 17:36.830
There's no one else here.

17:36.660 --> 17:38.110
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

17:37.830 --> 17:38.830
Who says there's no one else here?

17:38.130 --> 17:39.800
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

17:40.220 --> 17:41.440
♪ Incredible ♪

17:41.930 --> 17:42.940
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

17:43.560 --> 17:44.440
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

17:44.600 --> 17:46.260
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

17:46.510 --> 17:49.310
Greetings, Your Majesty.
Greetings, Your Highness.

17:46.600 --> 17:47.740
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

17:48.170 --> 17:49.490
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

17:49.840 --> 17:52.690
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

17:50.510 --> 17:51.070
These are

17:51.680 --> 17:52.930
my personal secret guards.

17:52.930 --> 17:54.520
♪ From day to night ♪

17:53.350 --> 17:53.720
Chu Yi

17:53.920 --> 17:54.660
specializes in Hard Qigong.

17:54.660 --> 17:56.090
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

17:56.180 --> 17:57.730
♪ From the present to the past ♪

17:57.030 --> 17:57.360
Chu Er

17:57.790 --> 17:58.480
specializes in hidden weapons.

17:57.850 --> 17:58.980
♪ It's always you ♪

17:59.470 --> 18:00.970
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

17:59.790 --> 18:00.200
Chu San

18:00.350 --> 18:01.070
has extraordinary flexibility.

18:00.990 --> 18:02.480
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

18:02.560 --> 18:05.480
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

18:02.750 --> 18:03.200
Chu Si.

18:04.440 --> 18:05.300
He's good at...

18:05.810 --> 18:08.910
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

18:06.640 --> 18:07.500
Using poisons.

18:08.110 --> 18:09.440
And Chu Wu, Chu Liu, Chu Qi...

18:08.960 --> 18:10.860
♪ With you ♪

18:10.000 --> 18:10.860
That's enough.

18:10.920 --> 18:11.550
No need for demonstrations.

18:11.460 --> 18:13.630
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

18:11.960 --> 18:13.560
No need for demonstrations.

18:13.660 --> 18:15.380
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

18:14.960 --> 18:15.880
All seven of them

18:15.420 --> 18:17.380
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

18:16.310 --> 18:16.770
will now

18:17.240 --> 18:18.110
be stationed at Zhaoyang Palace.

18:17.870 --> 18:20.160
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

18:18.830 --> 18:20.110
Do they

18:20.210 --> 18:21.720
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

18:21.070 --> 18:22.000
have no real names?

18:21.740 --> 18:23.760
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

18:23.240 --> 18:24.840
Names are merely code names.

18:25.350 --> 18:26.150
From today on,

18:27.110 --> 18:28.710
they will hide in the shadows

18:29.030 --> 18:30.000
and protect you

18:30.680 --> 18:31.740
as they protect me.

18:34.230 --> 18:35.730
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

18:35.820 --> 18:37.480
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

18:36.350 --> 18:37.350
Where's my snake?

18:46.070 --> 18:47.680
Does none of you care about me?

18:47.680 --> 18:51.340
Aren't you supposed to protect me
just as you protect His Majesty?

18:51.640 --> 18:52.700
It's just a reflex.

18:52.960 --> 18:54.620
Give them some time to adjust.

18:57.270 --> 19:00.070
Other people's staff
really can't be relied upon.

19:00.240 --> 19:02.100
I still need my own secret guards.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.640
Starting today,

19:03.920 --> 19:06.180
all of you will serve in Zhaoyang Palace.

19:06.680 --> 19:09.030
Remember to behave properly,

19:09.270 --> 19:10.830
be careful with your words and actions,

19:10.830 --> 19:12.830
and never do anything improper.

19:14.030 --> 19:15.090
Do you understand?

19:16.200 --> 19:17.270
At least answer me!

19:18.880 --> 19:19.550
Is it fun?

19:20.000 --> 19:20.920
Yes, it's fun.

19:21.200 --> 19:23.480
Your Majesty, push me higher!

19:23.480 --> 19:24.680
Not high enough?

19:24.880 --> 19:26.830
I want to fly!

19:25.530 --> 19:26.980
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

19:27.010 --> 19:28.600
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

19:28.110 --> 19:28.790
Okay!

19:28.990 --> 19:30.210
♪ Incredible ♪

19:30.590 --> 19:31.770
♪ The stars have shifted ♪

19:30.720 --> 19:31.510
Stop looking.

19:31.510 --> 19:32.170
Move along.

19:32.190 --> 19:33.220
♪ Fate is written in stone ♪

19:32.590 --> 19:33.350
Hurry up. Move.

19:33.300 --> 19:35.080
♪ Crossing time and space to meet you ♪

19:34.640 --> 19:35.680
-It's fun!
-Hurry up.

19:35.410 --> 19:36.430
♪ Pouting and squabbling ♪

19:36.960 --> 19:38.190
♪ Shocking and breathtaking ♪

19:37.790 --> 19:38.670
[Zhaoyang Hall]

19:38.680 --> 19:41.400
♪ Precisely into each other's hearts ♪

19:39.110 --> 19:40.030
Fly.

19:41.740 --> 19:43.320
♪ From day to night ♪

19:43.420 --> 19:44.930
♪ From lively to lonely ♪

19:44.990 --> 19:46.540
♪ From the present to the past ♪

19:46.610 --> 19:47.720
♪ It's always you ♪

19:46.680 --> 19:47.510
Your Majesty,

19:48.210 --> 19:50.070
this dried persimmon is delicious!

19:48.270 --> 19:49.700
♪ From misunderstanding to fascination ♪

19:49.770 --> 19:51.140
♪ From disgust to trust ♪

19:50.550 --> 19:51.010
Come on.

19:51.230 --> 19:54.240
♪ I'll search for you with all my might ♪

19:51.880 --> 19:52.940
My dear, you eat it.

19:53.270 --> 19:54.630
You eat it, Your Majesty.

19:54.630 --> 19:57.670
♪ Warm and carefree ♪

19:55.310 --> 19:56.370
My dear, you eat it.

19:57.160 --> 19:58.550
You eat it, Your Majesty.

19:57.760 --> 19:59.750
♪ With you ♪

19:58.590 --> 19:59.680
My dear, you eat it.

20:00.220 --> 20:02.540
♪ Love is your salt, your sugar ♪

20:02.630 --> 20:04.130
♪ Your flour, your sauce ♪

20:03.510 --> 20:05.070
I caught a fish!

20:04.200 --> 20:06.100
♪ Your grains and beans ♪

20:06.640 --> 20:08.900
♪ Love is sweet, sour, bitter and spicy ♪

20:07.750 --> 20:08.930
But I caught a bigger one.

20:08.930 --> 20:10.560
♪ A recipe of mixed flavors ♪

20:09.790 --> 20:10.450
Where is it?

20:10.580 --> 20:12.510
♪ A tender haven with you ♪

20:11.590 --> 20:12.250
Right here.

20:13.000 --> 20:13.600
A mermaid.

20:15.000 --> 20:15.960
Stop it!

20:15.960 --> 20:16.660
What's going on?

20:16.660 --> 20:18.110
♪ Love is a sweet recipe ♪

20:17.160 --> 20:18.240
Am I the only one who thinks

20:18.240 --> 20:20.400
Noble Consort Yu is too affected?

20:18.290 --> 20:19.830
♪ Slowly fermenting ♪

20:20.510 --> 20:22.160
You're not the only one.

20:26.000 --> 20:27.730
These past few days, Consort Yu

20:27.920 --> 20:29.920
has been waking up,

20:30.350 --> 20:31.410
having breakfast,

20:32.470 --> 20:34.130
then strolling in the garden,

20:34.350 --> 20:35.350
and having lunch.

20:39.400 --> 20:40.110
And then?

20:40.920 --> 20:44.250
She stays in her chambers
behind closed doors for six hours.

20:44.590 --> 20:45.590
Six hours?

20:46.310 --> 20:47.640
What has she been doing?

20:48.350 --> 20:49.590
Nothing much.

20:49.960 --> 20:50.820
Just sleeping.

20:50.880 --> 20:51.590
Sleeping?

20:54.960 --> 20:56.770
Eating, sleeping, rinse and repeat.

20:56.770 --> 20:58.830
She's got no worries at all, does she?

20:59.880 --> 21:00.550
What else?

21:02.030 --> 21:03.440
She also sends for her dinner,

21:03.440 --> 21:05.720
and even orders a midnight snack.

21:06.510 --> 21:08.110
What kind of person is she?

21:08.750 --> 21:10.200
She eats like a horse.

21:10.590 --> 21:12.200
Born in the Year of the Pig, I guess?

21:12.200 --> 21:13.790
She keeps to this routine every day.

21:13.790 --> 21:16.200
Are there no other changes with her?

21:16.510 --> 21:19.350
Well, there is one change.

21:19.400 --> 21:19.860
Tell me.

21:20.680 --> 21:22.340
Consort Yu's waist

21:22.640 --> 21:23.760
has widened a bit.

21:24.030 --> 21:25.350
What kind of person did you find for this?

21:25.350 --> 21:25.880
Get out!

21:26.640 --> 21:27.100
Get out!

21:27.200 --> 21:27.590
Yes.

21:38.830 --> 21:40.070
It's getting dark.

21:41.720 --> 21:43.180
How did I sleep for so long?

21:47.030 --> 21:47.490
Wanyin.

21:47.750 --> 21:48.350
Come here.

21:54.400 --> 21:54.800
You...

21:55.270 --> 21:56.250
When did you

21:56.440 --> 21:57.830
set up a barbecue?

21:58.350 --> 22:00.880
On high, we'd be two birds
flying wing to wing.

22:01.000 --> 22:01.530
On earth,

22:02.400 --> 22:03.930
let's just have a barbecue!

22:05.880 --> 22:06.750
Let's go fishing.

22:06.750 --> 22:07.280
Let's go.

22:07.350 --> 22:08.480
Let's go catch fish!

22:10.110 --> 22:11.680
We've been acting
in front of those eunuchs and maids

22:11.680 --> 22:12.830
for days now.

22:13.720 --> 22:15.440
I can't even spin in circles anymore.

22:15.440 --> 22:17.200
And even if there are spies among them,

22:17.200 --> 22:19.530
they must have lowered their guard by now.

22:19.790 --> 22:20.650
I'm not acting.

22:21.160 --> 22:22.960
I really want to have a barbecue.

22:22.960 --> 22:24.290
But I can't eat anymore.

22:25.480 --> 22:26.610
I've gained weight.

22:29.790 --> 22:31.250
What do you want to do then?

22:32.150 --> 22:33.270
Let's sneak out of the palace.

22:33.270 --> 22:33.830
What for?

22:35.270 --> 22:37.670
I've figured out
how to get past Prince Duan

22:37.830 --> 22:39.030
to fetch Xu Yao's book.

22:39.030 --> 22:39.830
Aren't we supposed to

22:39.830 --> 22:40.350
lay low?

22:41.240 --> 22:42.350
How boring that is!

22:43.110 --> 22:43.720
Let's just

22:44.640 --> 22:45.440
have some fun.

22:47.960 --> 22:49.400
Great!

22:57.640 --> 22:58.830
No one will recognize you.

22:58.830 --> 22:59.160
Look.

22:59.790 --> 23:00.450
No problem.

23:07.440 --> 23:09.480
Since ancient times,
beautiful women have caused trouble,

23:09.480 --> 23:13.010
just like the demonic consort
who's causing havoc in our state.

23:13.440 --> 23:13.750
Me?

23:13.790 --> 23:15.120
Since she gained favor,

23:15.480 --> 23:18.510
that tyrant has neglected
state affairs even more.

23:19.110 --> 23:21.790
All day long in the Zhaoyang Palace,

23:22.030 --> 23:23.640
-he's just making eyes at that consort...
-He's talking about me!

23:23.640 --> 23:24.900
And flirting with her.

23:27.110 --> 23:28.440
You may well wonder

23:29.110 --> 23:32.480
if she's pretty or a master of coquetry.

23:32.790 --> 23:35.320
Why does this demonic consort
have such power

23:35.550 --> 23:37.400
that the emperor refuses to leave her?

23:37.400 --> 23:38.930
It's actually very simple.

23:39.720 --> 23:40.780
It's all because of

23:40.920 --> 23:42.790
our specialty at Tianxiang House,

23:42.790 --> 23:44.000
Fish Ball Wine!

23:45.620 --> 23:46.200
You...

23:46.670 --> 23:48.600
Ladies, would you like to try some?

23:50.880 --> 23:53.400
It seems that our personas
are quite impressive.

23:53.400 --> 23:55.400
They're even selling merchandise of us.

23:55.400 --> 23:57.230
I was never this popular before.

23:57.510 --> 23:59.170
This is what we call bundling.

23:59.270 --> 24:00.270
I made you famous.

24:02.440 --> 24:03.970
I'm not complimenting you.

24:07.070 --> 24:08.930
How much longer do we have to walk?

24:09.200 --> 24:10.430
Isn't Xu Yao's book

24:10.790 --> 24:12.640
hidden in Prince Duan's mansion?

24:12.640 --> 24:14.840
Who told you we're out to steal the book?

24:14.960 --> 24:15.960
With our skills,

24:16.350 --> 24:18.280
plus your secret guards behind us,

24:18.880 --> 24:20.810
we'd just be walking to our deaths.

24:21.510 --> 24:23.240
So you're just out here for fun?

24:23.550 --> 24:25.350
Am I that shallow in your eyes?

24:26.400 --> 24:28.130
I'm taking you to meet someone,

24:28.270 --> 24:31.330
a master who exploits plot holes
in the original story.

24:31.680 --> 24:32.210
Let's go.

24:35.200 --> 24:36.400
Don't follow so closely.

24:36.400 --> 24:37.330
Spread out a bit.

24:37.590 --> 24:38.850
In typical web novels,

24:39.110 --> 24:40.270
there's always one

24:40.270 --> 24:42.240
incredibly powerful master.

24:42.830 --> 24:46.030
As it happens, this person
has deep connections with you.

24:46.070 --> 24:46.550
Who?

24:46.960 --> 24:47.880
Never heard of this person.

24:47.880 --> 24:49.140
Of course you haven't.

24:49.650 --> 24:52.330
[Bei Zhou]

24:49.920 --> 24:51.510
This person's name is Bei Zhou,

24:51.510 --> 24:53.310
who happens to be your mother...

24:54.310 --> 24:55.040
Your mother,

24:55.310 --> 24:57.920
the late Empress Ci Zhen's
childhood bodyguard.

24:57.920 --> 25:00.380
They grew up together
as childhood friends.

25:00.640 --> 25:02.350
Shortly after Empress Ci Zhen
entered the palace,

25:02.350 --> 25:03.280
she passed away.

25:03.720 --> 25:06.380
Bei Zhou believed
she was murdered by villains.

25:06.640 --> 25:07.000
So,

25:07.880 --> 25:09.200
he joined a martial arts sect

25:09.200 --> 25:10.880
and mastered
extraordinary fighting skills.

25:10.260 --> 25:13.020
[Martial Arts Hero Rankings]

25:12.070 --> 25:14.160
"Transmigration: The Demonic Consort"
states that

25:14.160 --> 25:16.020
he came back to the capital later,

25:16.110 --> 25:18.640
wanting to take
the son of his old friend, you,

25:19.110 --> 25:19.770
Xiahou Dan,

25:19.960 --> 25:20.760
away with him.

25:21.440 --> 25:22.720
But this person never came.

25:22.720 --> 25:23.380
He did come.

25:24.440 --> 25:25.350
But he came too late,

25:25.350 --> 25:27.280
only managing to take your corpse.

25:28.310 --> 25:29.070
Isn't that

25:29.720 --> 25:30.660
a bit too late?

25:31.510 --> 25:32.770
But now I know the plot.

25:33.160 --> 25:35.060
We can make him appear earlier.

25:35.310 --> 25:35.910
So where is

25:36.110 --> 25:36.840
this person?

25:39.440 --> 25:40.100
We're here.

25:42.030 --> 25:44.230
Spring water outshines the sky in blue.

25:44.790 --> 25:47.320
On painted barge,
I sleep to rain's soft tune.

25:47.720 --> 25:49.780
I'm but a mortal in the mundane world.

25:50.200 --> 25:52.530
I envy mandarin ducks, not the immortals.

25:53.550 --> 25:55.210
Young master, please come in.

25:56.480 --> 25:57.620
What a good poem!

25:57.790 --> 25:58.440
Let's go.

25:58.880 --> 25:59.790
-Look.
-What is this?

25:59.790 --> 26:00.440
Please come in.

26:00.440 --> 26:01.550
What is all this?

26:01.790 --> 26:03.830
Indulging in sensual pleasures
and wallowing in luxury,

26:03.830 --> 26:05.360
this is totally out of line!

26:05.680 --> 26:06.550
Put your hand down!

26:06.550 --> 26:08.010
You... put your hand down!

26:09.590 --> 26:09.960
Li.

26:10.350 --> 26:11.310
What if that person

26:10.800 --> 26:12.830
[Yang Duojie]

26:11.310 --> 26:12.680
you just pointed at and insulted

26:12.680 --> 26:14.440
is the son
of some important court official?

26:14.440 --> 26:14.830
That's right.

26:14.830 --> 26:16.590
I'm not afraid of his powerful father.

26:16.590 --> 26:18.190
I, Li Yunxi, have seen it all.

26:18.240 --> 26:18.790
Bearded man!

26:18.590 --> 26:20.630
[Li Yunxi]

26:19.720 --> 26:20.580
That's enough.

26:20.830 --> 26:22.310
It's rare for Yang to treat us today.

26:20.990 --> 26:24.270
[Wang Zhao]

26:22.880 --> 26:23.750
Look at you!

26:24.030 --> 26:25.270
Don't cause any trouble.

26:25.270 --> 26:27.480
It's not a treat. Watch your words.

26:27.960 --> 26:29.090
Just a little drink.

26:29.750 --> 26:31.750
I'd never afford a treat on my purse.

26:33.070 --> 26:34.480
Yang is treating us, right?

26:34.480 --> 26:35.240
Let's go quickly.

26:35.240 --> 26:35.640
Hurry up.

26:35.640 --> 26:36.400
What are you doing?

26:36.400 --> 26:37.240
I'm going to...

26:37.240 --> 26:38.240
I'm going to check it out.

26:38.240 --> 26:39.510
Entry before dusk hour

26:39.640 --> 26:40.700
enjoys a discount.

26:59.350 --> 26:59.920
Great!

27:02.480 --> 27:04.440
I thought it was some brothel.

27:04.880 --> 27:06.140
What are you thinking?

27:06.270 --> 27:07.400
You're the emperor.

27:07.440 --> 27:09.040
Can't you be more dignified?

27:16.660 --> 27:18.950
[Du Shan, Fine Fowls]
[Cheng Wen, Under the Blue Clouds]

27:18.950 --> 27:21.240
[Li Yunxi,
Intoxicated in the Shade of Flowers]

27:20.310 --> 27:21.310
In the storyline,

27:21.510 --> 27:22.750
this is where scholars and poets

27:22.750 --> 27:24.280
gather for elite meetings.

27:24.640 --> 27:25.440
See this sign?

27:26.240 --> 27:27.570
These songs listed here

27:27.720 --> 27:28.480
are performed by songstresses

27:28.480 --> 27:30.680
who set the most popular poems to music.

27:30.960 --> 27:33.680
It's basically
the ancient version of a book launch.

27:33.680 --> 27:34.940
Whoever has their poem

27:35.110 --> 27:37.040
sung by the most famous songstress

27:37.200 --> 27:38.920
becomes the most celebrated person.

27:38.920 --> 27:40.270
Li Bai and his kind often did this.

27:40.270 --> 27:41.670
They were truly refined.

27:43.400 --> 27:44.660
Scholars and poets...

27:46.110 --> 27:48.170
More like libertines than scholars,

27:48.240 --> 27:49.160
I'd say.

27:53.350 --> 27:54.160
Young man,

27:54.480 --> 27:57.270
you two look unfamiliar here.

27:59.440 --> 28:02.350
We heard Miss Hongyuan
is debuting a new song today,

28:02.590 --> 28:04.830
so we came to join in the fun.

28:04.830 --> 28:06.030
-No problem.
-Right?

28:06.510 --> 28:09.200
We want to witness
the birth of a new talent.

28:09.310 --> 28:12.510
Gentlemen, please go upstairs.
The view is better there.

28:15.550 --> 28:16.080
Brother.

28:17.000 --> 28:17.730
Don't be shy.

28:18.270 --> 28:19.110
Enjoy yourself.

28:19.110 --> 28:19.570
Please.

28:19.640 --> 28:20.170
Let's go.

28:20.720 --> 28:21.240
Come on.

28:23.200 --> 28:23.930
Don't be shy.

28:32.350 --> 28:34.210
Why are you so familiar with this?

28:34.440 --> 28:35.960
If you draft more proposals

28:35.960 --> 28:37.550
and create more presentations,
you'll understand.

28:37.550 --> 28:38.880
It's all part of the job.

28:40.480 --> 28:42.400
Beauty, I'm here!

28:47.720 --> 28:48.510
Aren't you...

28:48.510 --> 28:48.910
You...

28:50.750 --> 28:52.680
You've already set everything up?

28:53.400 --> 28:54.400
As the president,

28:55.000 --> 28:57.060
I need to have the big picture, right?

29:06.530 --> 29:08.250
[Du Shan, Fine Fowls]
[Cheng Wen, Under the Blue Clouds]

29:08.250 --> 29:09.980
[Li Yunxi,
Intoxicated in the Shade of Flowers]

29:10.200 --> 29:11.750
Everyone!

29:12.350 --> 29:15.590
Miss Hongyuan has selected a poem

29:15.750 --> 29:17.220
and composed a new melody.

29:17.750 --> 29:20.680
She will perform
after one incense stick burns down.

29:21.310 --> 29:24.920
Everyone, place your bets quickly!

29:23.930 --> 29:25.110
[Fang Wenshui] [Cheng Wen]
[Li Yunxi] [Du Shan]

29:25.790 --> 29:26.920
This is outrageous!

29:28.030 --> 29:29.110
The art of poetry

29:29.350 --> 29:31.150
should not be used for gambling!

29:31.830 --> 29:32.930
I submitted my poem

29:33.310 --> 29:35.000
so it would be heard throughout the land

29:35.000 --> 29:37.310
and serve as
a remonstration to the emperor.

29:37.310 --> 29:38.440
The present emperor

29:38.790 --> 29:39.850
is so incompetent.

29:40.590 --> 29:41.720
On our journey here,

29:42.310 --> 29:43.970
through thirteen provinces,

29:44.550 --> 29:46.310
we saw people
selling themselves to bury their fathers,

29:46.310 --> 29:48.770
countless families begging on the streets.

29:49.720 --> 29:51.680
"While meat and wine go to waste
behind the vermilion gates of the rich,

29:51.680 --> 29:53.000
the poor is frozen to death
on an empty stomach by the roadside."

29:53.000 --> 29:55.400
Such an incompetent ruler deserves to die!

29:56.070 --> 29:57.170
Li is right.

29:57.920 --> 29:58.980
The prosperity now

29:59.240 --> 30:00.830
-is nothing but an illusion
-Control yourself.

30:00.830 --> 30:02.270
-before the coming collapse.
-Control yourself.

30:02.270 --> 30:02.920
Nowadays

30:03.510 --> 30:05.200
there's no one capable in court.

30:05.200 --> 30:08.260
The Yan State has been eyeing
the Great Xia covetously.

30:08.310 --> 30:09.000
Even

30:09.640 --> 30:11.480
the tiny Qiang State

30:11.880 --> 30:13.540
dares to violate our borders.

30:13.750 --> 30:14.680
I've heard

30:15.020 --> 30:16.350
[Du Shan]

30:15.240 --> 30:17.370
the emperor now favors Yu exclusively

30:17.480 --> 30:19.270
and pays even less
attention to state affairs.

30:19.270 --> 30:20.470
That demonic consort

30:20.830 --> 30:23.690
brings disaster to the country
and kills innocents

30:24.110 --> 30:25.960
just like the infamous Daji.

30:26.750 --> 30:27.610
I heard her face

30:27.830 --> 30:29.110
is as sharp-featured as a snake spirit's,

30:29.110 --> 30:31.640
and her chin is so pointy
that it could peel a pear!

30:31.640 --> 30:32.900
My chin can peel a pear?

30:33.200 --> 30:34.270
I'll peel you now!

30:35.070 --> 30:36.130
Control yourself.

30:36.680 --> 30:37.740
Control yourself.

30:43.880 --> 30:45.480
There's no need to speak like that.

30:45.480 --> 30:47.270
"The songstress knows not
the grief of the captive king."

30:47.270 --> 30:49.170
Do they really sing of their own accord?

30:49.170 --> 30:50.720
It's clearly those wealthy young masters

30:49.280 --> 30:51.280
[Er Lan]

30:50.720 --> 30:52.480
who splash out a fortune to request them.

30:52.480 --> 30:54.410
Why lay the blame on women instead?

30:55.790 --> 30:57.200
This person's words make perfect sense.

30:57.200 --> 30:59.510
The most despicable
are those mindless lackeys

30:59.510 --> 31:00.570
who aid the tyrant.

31:00.640 --> 31:02.510
They cow the loyal officials into silence

31:02.510 --> 31:03.920
and let the treacherous ones
seize control of the court.

31:03.920 --> 31:05.790
If I pass the imperial exam, I'll
remonstrate at the cost of my life

31:05.790 --> 31:06.680
and eliminate those lackeys first.

31:06.680 --> 31:07.030
Li.

31:07.030 --> 31:08.110
-Li is right.
-Control yourself.

31:08.110 --> 31:10.970
-Let's control ourselves.
-You are our role model.

31:11.750 --> 31:13.160
You're always talking about death.

31:13.160 --> 31:14.400
It's such bad luck.

31:15.480 --> 31:17.200
Let's protect ourselves first

31:17.200 --> 31:19.060
and plan our next move carefully.

31:20.270 --> 31:21.200
Come, young man.

31:22.070 --> 31:22.920
It's alright.

31:26.030 --> 31:26.450
Wait!

31:28.620 --> 31:31.390
[Fang Wenshui] [Cheng Wen]
[Li Yunxi] [Du Shan]

31:36.200 --> 31:37.000
Have some tea.

31:47.960 --> 31:52.400
Green shadows dance,
the phoenix branch sways.

31:53.110 --> 31:58.070
Alone it perches, no common bird stays.

31:58.480 --> 32:03.200
High on the parasol, a clear breeze blows.

32:03.920 --> 32:07.960
The noble bird chooses its tree,
spreads its wings and goes.

32:08.240 --> 32:12.960
The wise have eyes
to tell false from true.

32:13.590 --> 32:18.240
The loyal minister chooses a worthy lord,
with a faithful heart.

32:19.000 --> 32:24.200
The road to high glory lies ahead for all.

32:24.440 --> 32:33.720
Choose the good to abide with,
wait for the time to call.

32:35.160 --> 32:37.000
Great!

32:37.350 --> 32:39.960
Excellent!

32:40.350 --> 32:41.920
What I sang today

32:42.200 --> 32:44.310
was composed by the talented Du Shan,

32:44.830 --> 32:45.960
a piece called Fine Fowls.

32:45.960 --> 32:47.070
Du, it was you?

32:47.550 --> 32:48.610
Congratulations!

32:48.830 --> 32:49.480
Thank you.

32:49.720 --> 32:52.110
I never thought a slacker like you

32:52.310 --> 32:54.110
could pen such incisive verses!

32:54.960 --> 32:55.830
I'm flattered.

32:58.270 --> 32:59.310
Wonderful!

32:59.880 --> 33:01.080
What's so wonderful?

33:01.480 --> 33:02.160
Don't you hear

33:02.160 --> 33:04.890
this poem is mocking me
for not being a wise ruler?

33:05.200 --> 33:05.960
I meant

33:07.310 --> 33:08.720
what a beautiful lady.

33:11.110 --> 33:12.510
Relax.

33:12.960 --> 33:13.790
When people talk like that,

33:13.790 --> 33:15.640
it means your tyrant image is solid,

33:15.640 --> 33:17.750
staying true to the original character.

33:17.750 --> 33:18.480
It also shows

33:19.270 --> 33:22.400
there are quite a few people
in the world who want me dead.

33:25.920 --> 33:26.880
Have you forgotten

33:26.880 --> 33:28.540
what you came here to do today?

33:29.680 --> 33:30.830
Have you found the person
you're looking for?

33:30.830 --> 33:31.090
I...

33:31.440 --> 33:32.500
How could I forget?

33:32.890 --> 33:33.950
I'm still looking.

33:36.030 --> 33:37.290
I just skimmed through

33:37.440 --> 33:39.000
the original novel.

33:39.550 --> 33:41.200
I can't remember the description

33:41.200 --> 33:43.030
of this person's appearance at all.

33:43.030 --> 33:44.270
With so many people here,

33:44.270 --> 33:45.530
can we really find him?

33:45.830 --> 33:46.550
I remember

33:47.070 --> 33:48.270
in the original book,

33:48.720 --> 33:50.450
you look a lot like your mother.

33:51.240 --> 33:52.270
Just stay like this.

33:52.270 --> 33:53.270
Stand right here.

33:53.270 --> 33:54.240
With your face

33:54.240 --> 33:56.070
being the spitting image of your mother's,

33:56.070 --> 33:57.130
I refuse to believe

33:57.640 --> 33:58.900
that we can't find him,

33:59.480 --> 34:00.810
or that he can't find us.

34:01.480 --> 34:02.310
Are you sure?

34:03.400 --> 34:04.860
My mother looks like this?

34:05.960 --> 34:06.980
Sorry.

34:07.510 --> 34:08.310
Just a moment.

34:14.000 --> 34:15.199
Come, let me tell you.

34:20.110 --> 34:21.170
That hurts so much.

34:21.360 --> 34:22.690
Just hurry and find him.

34:24.630 --> 34:25.440
That one definitely isn't him.

34:25.440 --> 34:26.050
Too fat.

34:26.590 --> 34:27.670
That one doesn't look right either.

34:27.670 --> 34:28.440
Too young.

34:29.400 --> 34:30.530
What about that one?

34:31.880 --> 34:32.920
Looks too sleazy.

34:34.510 --> 34:36.639
A fine fowl perches only on a fine tree.

34:36.880 --> 34:39.230
Du, your words truly resonate with me.

34:40.070 --> 34:42.230
But where on earth is such a fine tree

34:42.550 --> 34:44.710
to be found in this troubled world today?

34:44.710 --> 34:46.440
Actually, we've long heard that

34:46.440 --> 34:47.840
Prince Duan's
literary and military talents

34:47.840 --> 34:49.480
far exceed those of the tyrant.

34:49.480 --> 34:52.280
Moreover, Prince Duan
is known for respecting the talented,

34:52.280 --> 34:54.500
[Cen Jintian]

34:52.510 --> 34:54.880
appointing people based on merit,
regardless of background.

34:54.880 --> 34:56.710
If we want to fulfill our ambitions,

34:56.710 --> 34:57.230
perhaps...

34:57.230 --> 34:58.360
This is treasonous!

34:58.760 --> 34:59.690
How outrageous!

34:59.960 --> 35:00.850
Li!

35:01.070 --> 35:02.280
-Even if the emperor is incompetent,
-Li!

35:02.280 --> 35:04.190
he's still
the only legitimate ruler of the land.

35:04.190 --> 35:05.360
No matter how talented Prince Duan is,

35:05.360 --> 35:06.360
he should remain a subject.

35:06.360 --> 35:08.220
How could he overstep his bounds?

35:13.590 --> 35:14.390
What's wrong?

35:15.710 --> 35:16.310
Found him.

35:16.710 --> 35:17.110
Where?

35:19.360 --> 35:19.890
It's him.

35:22.280 --> 35:23.140
How do you know?

35:23.590 --> 35:24.190
Because

35:25.920 --> 35:28.880
he has eyes
that don't belong to a corporate slave.

35:30.960 --> 35:32.890
And look at that old man's temples.

35:33.320 --> 35:34.650
In martial arts novels,

35:34.960 --> 35:36.690
martial arts masters' temples

35:37.000 --> 35:38.330
are always protruding.

35:39.550 --> 35:41.000
Only the elderly

35:41.840 --> 35:43.370
and physically weak people

35:43.510 --> 35:45.150
have sunken temples.

35:46.440 --> 35:48.370
My great-uncle was just like that.

35:53.590 --> 35:55.190
If I remember correctly,

35:56.190 --> 35:58.120
that person who doesn't like music

35:58.360 --> 35:59.960
is also him, right?

36:04.370 --> 36:05.760
You have a good memory.

36:06.750 --> 36:07.320
Anyway,

36:07.430 --> 36:09.760
when he comes out,
you can test him and see.

36:10.320 --> 36:11.250
Why don't you go?

36:11.280 --> 36:13.060
If I go, wouldn't I
just be walking to my death?

36:13.060 --> 36:14.310
If anything happens to you,

36:14.310 --> 36:16.170
your guards will all protect you.

36:17.320 --> 36:17.920
My guards...

36:17.920 --> 36:18.850
He's coming out!

36:27.070 --> 36:27.440
Sir.

36:28.880 --> 36:29.590
How many

36:30.670 --> 36:32.800
waiters and servants do you have here?

36:32.840 --> 36:34.170
Seven or eight waiters,

36:34.320 --> 36:36.580
and roughly the same number of servants.

36:37.840 --> 36:38.800
Is there anyone

36:41.030 --> 36:43.000
who just arrived in the past two years,

36:43.000 --> 36:44.110
over 40 years old,

36:44.800 --> 36:46.330
and quite sturdy-looking?

36:50.000 --> 36:51.230
Why are you asking about this?

36:51.230 --> 36:53.290
I just find your face quite familiar.

36:55.360 --> 36:56.890
What about me, in your eyes?

37:09.800 --> 37:10.730
This bodes well.

37:15.290 --> 37:16.750
Meeting like this is fate.

37:17.480 --> 37:18.410
Since we've met,

37:19.030 --> 37:21.160
why don't we be honest with each other?

37:35.230 --> 37:36.630
Even if you're mistaken,

37:36.880 --> 37:38.810
there's no need to pull out a knife.

37:41.070 --> 37:42.070
A fight broke out!

37:46.840 --> 37:47.280
Let's go.

37:47.280 --> 37:48.110
Hurry!

37:49.480 --> 37:50.030
Look!

37:50.190 --> 37:51.510
It seems like there's a fight upstairs.

37:51.510 --> 37:52.440
There really is.

37:53.190 --> 37:55.190
There's actually a fight upstairs.

37:59.320 --> 38:01.250
You haven't paid yet. Don't leave!

38:02.630 --> 38:03.880
If you want to fight, do it outside!

38:03.880 --> 38:04.940
Not in here!

38:09.110 --> 38:11.320
Your guards seem rather incompetent.

38:27.960 --> 38:29.690
I mistook you for someone else.

38:30.200 --> 38:31.440
It's a misunderstanding.

38:31.440 --> 38:32.660
It's all a misunderstanding.

38:32.660 --> 38:33.190
Sorry.

38:34.430 --> 38:35.030
Sorry.

38:35.360 --> 38:36.060
Sorry.
